parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical Charge Build-up in Ignition Console
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical charge build-up in the ignition console can cause unexpected door lock behavior, which can lead to safety issues, such as doors opening while driving.

strong odor of fuel inside and outside the vehicle.
